dmca.title: Photographic Model Requests Removal of Images from Google
dmca.body:
Dear Google
 
Please remove the following images from your search engine.  They have appeared here without my permission.  I have searched the host site and believe that the images are 'dead links'.  I cannot find the said images on the website.
 
Also, I have emailed the website to notify them that if images are held on the website to remove them.
 
I enclose my official notification to you below and the URLs at the end of the email and as an attachment.  I would appreciate you removing the images as soon as possible.  Please contact me if you have any queries.
 
"I swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is accurate and that, for each image identified above, I either own the copyright or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed." 
 
Yours truly
[Private]
 
URLs FOR REMOVAL x 3:
